sub_title: Live Operations Specialist at Just Eat Takeaway.com
summary:
My latest big achievement has been to find the courage to leave Rome. I never thought I was the kind of person that leaves, but apparently I surprised myself. I wonder how I will surprise myself next time.  

Some of my skills are:
Passionate worker
Proactive approach. 
Team player
I enjoy to find solutions to unexpected challenges 
Creative
I'm hungry. 

I'm looking for an honest, positive working environment, with real growing career possibilities. 


I'm fluent in English (C2) and a native Italian speaker 
(next steps are going to be Nederlands and Español) 

My hobbies are: basketball and sports, baked cheesecakes, watching operas (especially Tosca), playing with any dog I see.
